improvements.title: Implement Semantic Kernel-based Frequency Router
improvements.description: Create a cognitive frequency router that uses SK to determine which cognitive frequency is best for a given task based on economic value
improvements.justification: Current frequency routing is manual and could benefit from AI-powered decision making

improvements.title: Add Adaptive Learning for Frequency Thresholds
improvements.description: Implement an adaptive learning system that automatically adjusts frequency thresholds based on past performance
improvements.justification: Static thresholds don't adapt to changing conditions and task types

improvements.title: Integrate with Semantic Kernel Memory for Goal History
improvements.description: Use SK Memory to store and retrieve past goals and their outcomes to inform future decisions
improvements.justification: The system currently doesn't learn from past goal executions
